msgid "Catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ, catunnaṃ sammappadhānānaṃ, catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ, pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ, pañcannaṃ balānaṃ, sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ, ariyassa aṭṭhaṅgikassa maggassa. "
msgstr "The four kinds of mindfulness meditation, the four right efforts, the four bases of psychic power, the five faculties, the five powers, the seven awakening factors, and the noble eightfold path. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.127, sc4
msgctxt "an7.71:4.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, kukkuṭiyā aṇḍāni aṭṭha vā dasa vā dvādasa vā. "
msgstr "Suppose there was a chicken with eight or ten or twelve eggs. "

msgctxt "an7.71:4.2"
msgid "Tānassu kukkuṭiyā sammā adhisayitāni, sammā pariseditāni, sammā paribhāvitāni. "
msgstr "And she properly sat on them to keep them warm and incubated. "

msgctxt "an7.71:4.3"
msgid "Kiñcāpi tassā kukkuṭiyā na evaṃ icchā uppajjeyya: "
msgstr "Even if that chicken doesn’t wish: "

msgctxt "an7.71:4.4"
msgid "‘aho vata me kukkuṭapotakā pādanakhasikhāya vā mukhatuṇḍakena vā aṇḍakosaṃ padāletvā sotthinā abhinibbhijjeyyun’ti, "
msgstr "‘If only my chicks could break out of the eggshell with their claws and beak and hatch safely!’ "

msgctxt "an7.71:4.5"
msgid "atha kho bhabbāva te kukkuṭapotakā pādanakhasikhāya vā mukhatuṇḍakena vā aṇḍakosaṃ padāletvā sotthinā abhinibbhijjituṃ. "
msgstr "Still they can break out and hatch safely. "

msgctxt "an7.71:4.6"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "an7.71:4.7"
msgid "Tathā hi, bhikkhave, kukkuṭiyā aṇḍāni sammā adhisayitāni, sammā pariseditāni, sammā paribhāvitāni. "
msgstr "Because she properly sat on them to keep them warm and incubated. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.71:4.8"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhāvanaṃ anuyuttassa bhikkhuno viharato kiñcāpi na evaṃ icchā uppajjeyya: "
